This is dedicated to the prettiest one...such unavoidable conclusions. growing in backward motion, a blind understanding with cold lips to kiss. demonstrate the divine. attempting the impossible. we'll never be like that...didn't we say "it will never die?" such a sexual mystery. unspoken, precious and rejected, let it be perfectly clear, silently my dear. demonstrate the devine. attempting the impossible. the truth is bound to lie somewhere far from fleeting. unspoken, cruder than a villain, the imitator. we'll never be like that...didn't we say "it will never die?" this is forever. where does it arise and where does it lead? she is filled with secrets, dwells at the heart of...